### LexicalNode.exportJSON()

Source: https://github.com/facebook/lexical/blob/main/packages/lexical-website/docs/concepts/serialization.md

Controls how a LexicalNode is represented as JSON by adding an exportJSON() method. It's important to extend the serialization of the superclass by invoking super.

```APIDOC
## LexicalNode.exportJSON()

### Description
Controls how a `LexicalNode` is represented as JSON by adding an `exportJSON()` method. Extend the serialization of the superclass by invoking `super`.

### Method
```
exportJSON(): SerializedLexicalNode
```

### Request Example
```json
{
  "type": "myNode",
  "version": 1
}
```

### Response
#### Success Response (200)
- **type** (string) - The type of the node.
- **version** (number) - The version of the node serialization.

### Response Example
```json
{
  "type": "myNode",
  "version": 1,
  "customProperty": "example"
}
```
```

